<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٦٢٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6006">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يُوسُفَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6437">مُوسَى بْنِ عُقْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2249">سَالِمٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَتْ يَمِينُ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٢٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَسَلَّمَ:</span> لَا وَمُقَلِّبِ الْقُلُوبِ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>